<body>
<!--if resume.id_user ==undefined ให้แสดงหน้าaddแต่ถ้าไม่ให้แสดงhistory -->
<%- include('navbar') %>
<% if(resume) { %>
  <form action="/user/addresume/<%= user.id_user %>" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">

    <div class="inputbox-regis">
      <input type="text" id="professional_summary"  name="professional_summary" />
      <label for="professional_summary">professional_summary</label>
    </div>
    <div class="inputbox-regis">
     <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
     <input type="text" id="work_experience" name= "work_experience" />
     <label for="work_experience">work_experience</label>
      </div>




      <div class="inputbox-regis">
        <input type="text" id="skills"  name="skills" />
        <label for="skills">skills</label>
      </div>
      <div class="inputbox-regis">
       <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
       <input type="text" id="education" name= "education"/>
       <label for="education">education</label>
        </div>



        <div class="inputbox-regis">
          <input type="text" id="languages"  name="languages"  />
          <label for="languages">languages</label>
        </div>
        <div class="inputbox-regis">
         <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
         <input type="text" id="interests" name= "interests" />
         <label for="interests">interests</label>
          </div>

          <div class="inputbox-regis">
            <input type="text" id="contact"  name="contact"  />
            <label for="contact">contact</label>
          </div>
        
        <!-- <div class="inputbox-regis">
          <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
          <input type="password" id="password" autocomplete="off" required>
          <label for="password">Password</label>
        </div> -->
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">save</button>

      </form>
<% } else { %>

 <form action="/user/updateresume/<%= user.id_user %>" method="post">

    <div class="inputbox-regis">
      <input type="text" id="professional_summary"  name="professional_summary" value="<%= resume.professional_summary %>" />
      <label for="professional_summary">professional_summary</label>
    </div>
    <div class="inputbox-regis">
     <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
     <input type="text" id="work_experience" name= "work_experience"value="<%= resume.work_experience %>" />
     <label for="work_experience">work_experience</label>
      </div>




      <div class="inputbox-regis">
        <input type="text" id="skills"  name="skills" value="<%= resume.skills %>" />
        <label for="skills">skills</label>
      </div>
      <div class="inputbox-regis">
       <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
       <input type="text" id="education" name= "education"value="<%= resume.education %>" />
       <label for="education">education</label>
        </div>



        <div class="inputbox-regis">
          <input type="text" id="languages"  name="languages" value="<%= resume.languages %>" />
          <label for="languages">languages</label>
        </div>
        <div class="inputbox-regis">
         <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
         <input type="text" id="interests" name= "interests"value="<%= resume.interests %>" />
         <label for="interests">interests</label>
          </div>

          <div class="inputbox-regis">
            <input type="text" id="contact"  name="contact" value="<%= resume.contact %>" />
            <label for="contact">contact</label>
          </div>
        
        <!-- <div class="inputbox-regis">
          <ion-icon name="mail-outline"></ion-icon>
          <input type="password" id="password" autocomplete="off" required>
          <label for="password">Password</label>
        </div> -->
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">save</button>

      </form>
<% } %>
<script>

  $.Thailand({
    $district: $('#district_company'), // input ของตำบล//ใช้idแต่ละinput
    $amphoe: $('#amphoe'), // input ของอำเภอ ยังไม่มีในdb
    $province: $('#province_company'), // input ของจังหวัด
    $zipcode: $('#zipcode_company'), // input ของรหัสไปรษณีย์
  });

</script>
</body>

</html>